===Noun===
'''rafsi''' (rafsi: '''raf''')

# [[affix]]

====Usage notes====
''rafsi'' are the affix-forms (the [[combining]]-forms) for Lojban words or concepts. E.g., the ''rafsi'' for the word ''rafsi'' is ''raf''.

